entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You finished the test of navigation in time.
entries.journal_entry_description: An'Kwee wants you to try a smaller course with tighter turns. If you fail the race you may speak to Draknus or the race droid to take the race again.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: An'Kwee wants you to prove your navigation skills. Race the course in the required time. Check in with the race timer to start the race.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Check In with the Race Timer to Start Race
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 1 before the timer runs out.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 2 before the timer runs out.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 3 before the timer runs out.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 4 before the timer runs out.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Talk to the race timer to check your time.
